data.description:
Welcome to your dream home in 2023! This stunning two-level residence features four bedrooms and three bathrooms, providing ample space for comfortable living. As you enter, you'll immediately notice the attention to detail and luxurious finishes throughout. The main floor is thoughtfully designed with convenience in mind. The primary bedroom, strategically located on this level, offers a private retreat. Connected to the primary bedroom is an exquisite ensuite bathroom, boasting dual vanities for added functionality, a relaxing soaker tub, and all the modern fixtures you could desire.

On the same floor, you'll find a well-appointed guest bedroom, providing a comfortable space for visitors or family members. The main level also features a spacious living room, complete with a cozy gas fireplace, creating the perfect ambiance for relaxation and gatherings.

The kitchen in this home is truly a chef's delight. It comes fully equipped with stainless steel appliances, including a gas range that allows for precise and efficient cooking. The kitchen's centerpiece is a large island, adorned with elegant quartz countertops, providing ample space for meal preparation, dining, and entertaining.

Venturing to the second level, you'll discover a versatile loft space that can be utilized as a home office, a play area, or even a media room. This flexible space offers endless possibilities to suit your lifestyle.

Exterior features of this home include double porches, enhancing the curb appeal and providing an inviting space to enjoy the outdoors. Additionally, a two-car garage ensures convenience and ample storage for vehicles and other belongings.

Throughout the main level, the home boasts crown molding, adding a touch of sophistication to each room. To further enhance the exterior aesthetics and functionality, shutters have been installed, adding character and privacy.

Coosaw Point, a prestigious residential community nestled in a serene coastal setting, offers an array of luxurious amenities designed to enhance the residents' leisure and recreational experiences. Situated on the breathtaking Coosaw Point River, the community boasts a remarkable range of facilities, including a pool, river house, tennis courts, dock, and boat launch.
